    "title": "Modifier Placement",
    "body": "An introductory phrase must modify the noun that immediately follows it. If it doesn't, the modifier 'dangles' and the sentence says something illogical. Place the right noun right after the phrase.",
    "key_points": [
      "Put the modified noun right after the phrase.",
      "Check that the opening phrase logically fits that noun.",
      "Dangling modifiers create unintended meanings."
    ]
